Requires-Dist: pygments>=2.14

# vellum-pygments

A minimal [Pygments](https://pygments.org/) lexer for **Vellum** (`.vel`), used by this repo’s MkDocs site.

Install with the main project’s `requirements-docs.txt` (`-e ./tools/vellum-pygments`).

In Markdown, use fenced code with language tag `vellum` or `vel`.
